@startuml sequence_recovery
!theme plain
title Password Recovery

actor User
participant "RecoverPage" as RP
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "RecoveryHandler" as H
participant "UserManager" as UM
participant "EmailSender" as ES

User -> RP: submit email
RP -> AC: POST /api/auth/recovery
AC -> H: Send(RequestRecoveryCommand)
H -> UM: GeneratePasswordResetTokenAsync
H -> ES: SendAsync(reset link)
H --> AC: ok
AC --> RP: 200 generic

== later ==
participant "ResetPage" as RPS
User -> RPS: open reset link, submit new password
RPS -> AC: POST /api/auth/reset
AC -> H: Send(ResetPasswordCommand)
H -> UM: ResetPasswordAsync
H -> UM: UpdateSecurityStampAsync (invalidates other sessions)
H --> AC: ok
AC --> RPS: 200
RPS --> User: navigate /auth/sign-in
@enduml
